        <h1>About Time Table Management System</h1>
        <p>
            The Time Table Management System is a comprehensive solution designed to help educational institutions and organizations manage their schedules efficiently. It enables administrators to organize classes, allocate teachers, manage time slots, and avoid conflicts in scheduling.
        </p>
        <p>
            This system streamlines the process of time table creation, allowing for automatic scheduling and manual adjustments to ensure optimal usage of available resources. With the Time Table Management System, both students and teachers can easily access their schedules, view updates in real time, and avoid conflicts in their classes and appointments.
        </p>
        <p>
            The system supports the following key features:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Automated generation of time tables based on predefined rules</li>
            <li>Conflict detection and resolution for overlapping schedules</li>
            <li>Admin control for managing classes, teachers, and rooms</li>
            <li>Student and teacher portals for viewing their schedules</li>
            <li>Real-time notifications for schedule changes</li>
            <li>Flexible customization to meet the specific needs of any institution</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            Our goal is to simplify the process of managing academic schedules, reduce the administrative burden, and provide a user-friendly interface for all users.
        </p>

